## ðŸ” Overview

HypnoNeuroToken (HNT) is a utility token powering the **HypnoNeuro gamified healing platform**. It supports the decentralized reward system for:

- Player progress in therapeutic rooms  
- NFT-based milestones (Mind Mastery NFTs)  
- Practitioner payments and premium services  
- Discounts and token-based session booking  

Built using OpenZeppelinâ€™s secure ERC-20 structure, HNT includes:

- ðŸ” `Ownable` â€” restricts minting/burning/pausing to the platform owner  
- ðŸ”„ `ERC20Pausable` â€” enables emergency transfer freezes  
- ðŸ”¨ Minting: Controlled token creation  
- ðŸ”¥ Burning: Voluntary token removal by users  
- â¸ Pausing: Emergency shutdown of token transfers  

